{"tid":2143683,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[又爭] 鄭松泰：本黨是第一個政黨在瘟疫初期在街頭派發口罩，並開街站呼籲大眾勤洗手，注意衛生。","createTime":"2020-08-07T08:38:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T14:48:34.000Z","uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"521f7ac012a569f68e2a81fae587932e4b25a890","tid":2143683,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:38:30.000Z","msg":"Chung-Tai Cheng 鄭松泰<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/s960x960/116923099_1585559951618356_8287981649126053873_o.jpg?_nc_cat=105&amp;_nc_sid=110474&amp;_nc_ohc=mx8DOTkYIj4AX_b97vf&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-1.fna&amp;_nc_tp=7&amp;oh=f1747420358d8ae846ec569b4753a529&amp;oe=5F53D848\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fs960x960%2F116923099_1585559951618356_8287981649126053873_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D105%26_nc_sid%3D110474%26_nc_ohc%3Dmx8DOTkYIj4AX_b97vf%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-1.fna%26_nc_tp%3D7%26oh%3Df1747420358d8ae846ec569b4753a529%26oe%3D5F53D848&h=b770bc2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果今年立法會選舉沒有延期，真正的選舉議題踏入8月才開始備受關注，就是「鳩帶口罩（用呢個「帶」字，因為並非戴上）」及「不要鳩戴口罩」之分。<br />\n<br />\n我早已準備好，當建制、泛民、黃色選舉候選人質疑為什麼我們主張「不戴口罩」，<span class=\"gold\">我便舉這個牌說明，本黨是第一個政黨在瘟疫初期在街頭派發口罩，並開街站呼籲大眾勤洗手，注意衛生。</span><br />\n<br />\n註：瘟疫政治下的經濟大蕭條、專權利用瘟疫恐懼壓抑人權等，這些議題卻被忽視 #香港點解搞成咁。"},{"pid":"5383b07346a2b1843b7d95c31fabbe8e5b3f4607","tid":2143683,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:38:40.000Z","msg":"[有圖] 熱狗用咩理由拒絕戴口罩？（患病/殘疾/困擾/避免受傷害）<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fKAtdS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fKAtdS</a><br />\n<br />\n熱狗係咪已經放棄戴口罩？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fEgwLS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fEgwLS</a><br />\n<br />\n熱狗：唔好出街呀，躲喺屋企啦。你仲要成日戴罩呀，訓教沖涼都要戴呀，唔係既話會被感染架，增加香港醫療負擔架。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2098271\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2098271</a><br />\n<br />\n啲熱狗係威係勢呢兩日去到沙田咪又係帶返口罩。。。。。。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2099363\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2099363</a><br />\n<br />\n鄭松泰談国歌法：我曾在北京生活5年，博士學位在北大取得，論黨的語言比謝偉俊更熟悉<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fHCspS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fHCspS</a><br />\n<br />\n鄭松泰不點名針對有區議員躲在天橋協助警察捉拿非法賽車<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2115237\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2115237</a>"},{"pid":"683f75b398e21bc7ceec3be71f51e3d9e3785818","tid":2143683,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:39:07.000Z","msg":"鄭松泰：理智防疫<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20200807/s00046/b2f7144ca768694cf3e482b81daa4c08.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20200807%2Fs00046%2Fb2f7144ca768694cf3e482b81daa4c08.jpg&h=519adfcf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e1c9f6a33ab3d8eff0f29aac6194ef15b2158360","tid":2143683,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"683f75b398e21bc7ceec3be71f51e3d9e3785818","tid":2143683,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:39:07.000Z","msg":"鄭松泰：理智防疫<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20200807/s00046/b2f7144ca768694cf3e482b81daa4c08.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20200807%2Fs00046%2Fb2f7144ca768694cf3e482b81daa4c08.jpg&h=519adfcf&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:39:29.000Z","msg":"註：小弟戴的不是KF94，是某個 Made in Hong Kong 的牌子，比較厚身，長戴會有點焗呢。"},{"pid":"b16da1f525a68c567c46a991618830a713e4b953","tid":2143683,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:39:57.000Z","msg":"鄭錦滿<br />\n1 天 &middot; <br />\n好多人因為各種原因，係不適宜戴口罩嘅，例如對口罩物料敏感、戴住呼吸困難、患自閉症兒童等等。<br />\n<br />\n而其實，好多香港人每日都已經戴住假面具做人，而家仲要強制多戴個口罩做道具，就無謂時刻狙擊唔戴、冇戴、或只係拉低口罩抖抖氣嘅人吧。"},{"pid":"9f0a62bd5a72605a883a44bb1617db03adabf516","tid":2143683,"uid":73381,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:40:13.000Z","msg":"健哥仲要派勁高質3M口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc92Bzpj.jpg&amp;h=033b9baf&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"adff1c4c2b666365eb5dbb871f3d3f8d2f4cdb6c","tid":2143683,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:41:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/p720x720/116584032_1195842870773119_227312211227469277_o.jpg?_nc_cat=106&amp;_nc_sid=110474&amp;_nc_ohc=GHAgNt7q1fkAX-wTfxG&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-2.fna&amp;_nc_tp=6&amp;oh=d0706d2c540499f94ccddfec4ecbed8b&amp;oe=5F51AF3E\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fp720x720%2F116584032_1195842870773119_227312211227469277_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D106%26_nc_sid%3D110474%26_nc_ohc%3DGHAgNt7q1fkAX-wTfxG%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-2.fna%26_nc_tp%3D6%26oh%3Dd0706d2c540499f94ccddfec4ecbed8b%26oe%3D5F51AF3E&h=7dcf9cb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf461bb7158c6ba6fd1e131818206fe6bc87f65b","tid":2143683,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:42:08.000Z","msg":"推死熱狗"},{"pid":"b4d0c714e698f5d17244b8a8ed8e12cc2538f69d","tid":2143683,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f0a62bd5a72605a883a44bb1617db03adabf516","tid":2143683,"uid":73381,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:40:13.000Z","msg":"健哥仲要派勁高質3M口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc92Bzpj.jpg&amp;h=033b9baf&amp;s=540\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:46:38.000Z","msg":"<em>2020年1月30日<br />\n<br />\n警方澄清傳言<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  別有用心人士再次在網上發放假消息，指各區警署會向市民免費派發口罩，又聲稱政府將會派發大量口罩予警察家屬。警方澄清絶無此事，市民切勿誤信假消息。<br />\n<br />\n民政事務總署澄清傳言<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  就網上及手機即時通訊軟件流傳信息，指各區民政諮詢中心及民政事務總署將向全港市民派發口罩，民政事務總署發言人今日（一月三十日）澄清絕無其事，並提醒市民加強警惕，勿輕信謠言。<br />\n<br />\n政府物流服務署澄清傳言<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  網上流傳謠言，指政府於口罩存倉地點向市民免費派發口罩，又指由昨日（一月二十九日）起以實名制供市民登記提取。政府物流服務署發言人今日（一月三十日）澄清絕無其事，並提醒市民加強警惕，勿輕信謠言。</em><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66b687db5e9249f409e2f73ef6bfdfb2834d7dfb","tid":2143683,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf461bb7158c6ba6fd1e131818206fe6bc87f65b","tid":2143683,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:42:08.000Z","msg":"推死熱狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:58:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5045b68c55d2120d18d1ec65ff9ea6720147c9d8","tid":2143683,"uid":64953,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T09:31:49.000Z","msg":"熱狗同中國一樣成日贏咁點得"},{"pid":"eb2c572645952250ffc0e91e8fa33882e1d199d8","tid":2143683,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5045b68c55d2120d18d1ec65ff9ea6720147c9d8","tid":2143683,"uid":64953,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T09:31:49.000Z","msg":"熱狗同中國一樣成日贏咁點得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T09:37:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91d8e39fa069721a64c66e0c10766e20bcf64986","tid":2143683,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T14:48:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"5045b68c55d2120d18d1ec65ff9ea6720147c9d8","tid":2143683,"uid":64953,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T09:31:49.000Z","msg":"熱狗同中國一樣成日贏咁點得"}}